title: 2 Bedroom in Lekki
description: Welcome to this beautifully modern 3-bedroomduplex in the heart of Lekki Phase 1, Lagos. Designed for comfort and style, this property features a spacious open-concept living room, a fully fitted kitchen with premium appliances, and three en-suite bedrooms that ensure privacy and convenience. The master bedroom offers a walk-in closet and a private balcony, while the outdoor space includes parking for 2 vehicles within a gated compound. With close proximity to top schools, shopping malls, and recreational areas, this home is ideal for families or professionals looking for convenience, security, and a premium lifestyle.
